              microglial regulome underlying AD genetic risk, and provide a
              functional framework to refine noncoding variant interpretation
              and therapeutic target discovery.",
  year     =  2025,
  url      = "https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/2025.10.13.25337902v1.abstract",
  keywords = {Submitted}
}

